To cite Max-Plus Algebra Toolbox for Matlab in publications use:

 Jaroslaw Stanczyk (2016)
 Max-Plus Algebra Toolbox for Matlab ver.1.7
 URL http://gen.up.wroc.pl/stanczyk/mpa/

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is:

@book{,
    author = {Jaroslaw Stanczyk},
    title  = {{Max-Plus Algebra Toolbox for Matlab} version 1.7},
    year   = {2016},
    url    = {http://gen.up.wroc.pl/stanczyk/mpa/},
}

Please cite Max-Plus Algebra Toolbox for Matlab when using it.
